(1) employees of the AT&T Benefits and/or AT&T Executive Compensation organizations responsible

for administering group health plan benefits under the HIPAA Plan, including those employees whose functions in the regular course of business include Payment, Health Care Operations or other matters pertaining to the health care programs under a HIPAA Plan;

(2) employees who supervise the work of the employees described in (1), above;

